{"tid":1702491,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"緊要，緊要，區議會需要大家幫手","createTime":"2019-11-09T17:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:19:02.000Z","uid":10881,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d81a1bdd90c42bf3071f16990faace94ad2554e9","tid":1702491,"uid":10881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:08:55.000Z","msg":"之前一直聽，<br />\n好多時都係叫大家，<br />\n見到代表香港人既候選人，<br />\n記得去幫手打下氣。<br />\n<br />\n實情係，<br />\n大家有時間，應該去問下需唔需要義工。<br />\n本人係一名啱啱grad 左無耐既番工狗<br />\n發覺可以幫手既時間好少，得番工前番工後。<br />\n如果大學中學手足可以幫到下手，<br />\n係我地幫唔到手既時間，做義工，<br />\n向D 街坊宣傳下候選人政綱，<br />\n屌下建制派，<br />\n相信會好有用。<br />\n<br />\n大家參與抗爭既時候唔好唔記得，<br />\n搶區議會議席都好緊要，<br />\n當中涉及好多利益輸送，資源，<br />\n仲有對街坊既宣傳教育推廣等。<br />\n多個企我地依邊既人當選，絕對好緊要。<br />\n幫手做義工既時間，絕對值得花！"},{"pid":"7e6ca11b721edc45acd838832b5e8a22796d5937","tid":1702491,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借個位黎唔該<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府會成立獨立調查委員會咁又點？五大訴求係咩？下一句係咩？唔記得哂？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6d1fecad4a1d76d923c04500ceab0ea9bee6ef45","tid":1702491,"uid":211004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43e229793168f9267524ac20efd8d4c88c9ad68a","tid":1702491,"uid":334448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:13:06.000Z","msg":"P牌仔假推"},{"pid":"506f0b85fb3bed709db174a17bd2d67963bce8d3","tid":1702491,"uid":211004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:28:01.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"c8c0b4e32d5eaed3f9d1fad2f91d0de37b4ee05d","tid":1702491,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T20:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d911388cbf18dbcff5038320d19d26acfebb7bf","tid":1702491,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB